  Icon: {fileID: 1208347981, guid: b2407ce4cf73ad348aec15ba9990f7a1, type: 3}
  Description: "Wound: An Ottoman arrow embedded deep in the chest, every breath
    rattling, foam at the lips.\n\nStory: Jean, a French knight of noble blood, clutches
    a tiny locket with his sister\u2019s portrait. Between coughs of red, he apologizes
    for abandoning her in France, swearing that he should have stayed to protect
    her instead of chasing glory here. His armor gleams, but it cannot shield him
    from the slow drowning inside his lungs.\n\nRequired bandages to heal: 5"
  slotNumber: 2
  requiredResource: Bandage
  requiredAmount: 5
